            "citations": null,
            "text": "{\"correctness\":{\"rating\":\"partial\",\"justification\":\"Most positions listed are correct and supported by the curriculum context. However, the answer conflates two separate entries: the profile text states the PPgSC coordination was 2006–2010, while the 'Atuação Profissional' section lists the same role as '05/2006 – Atual', creating confusion. The answer also includes 'Direção e administração no Centro de Ciências Exatas' as a vague separate entry, which is actually the same PPgSC coordination entry. The 'Diretora de Secretaria Regionais (SBC)' is an SBC role, not a university administrative position, though it is a legitimate administrative role. No factually wrong claims, but some imprecision and redundancy.\"},\"completeness\":{\"rating\":\"partial\",\"justification\":\"The answer covers the main administrative positions (PPgSC coordinator, Vice-Coordenadora do Curso de Ciências da Computação, LCC coordinator, SBC Diretora de Secretarias Regionais). However, it omits the role of Vice-Diretora Executiva at LARC (2005–2008), and does not mention the council representation roles (CONSEPE, CONSUNI) which are administrative in nature. The answer acknowledges it could list committee roles but does not include them.\"}}",
